ragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d91c168c-5077-4968-b943-bf6a39824ef8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-96a42b2a-78e4-4e25-b091-e757e1c5a0c6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">-------------------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9432eeb1-6071-4846-b92b-99ebc7613295\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fa228c55-6741-4060-a00d-39b8a9e094c7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>A4 사이즈와 접지 관하여</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1fa887dc-44d4-4ca2-b5bf-acea262d10bc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-918efef8-043c-4eb7-8235-8024c2974a8b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">-------------------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-03ec6b25-3caf-4a1b-a0e6-7ecf2e5efe0d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0aefdb7c-9bc9-4946-8bad-64213d4bf1bd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">원래 A4는 210mm × 297mm입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9b517de4-2fcc-481c-b5b6-bb71f9d136d4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-66c62520-825a-4e2f-b8d6-7795419dd1f8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">297mm를 3등분 하면 99mm입니다. 하지만 접힐 때 1mm 정도를 줄여서 안쪽으로 접히는 부분은 98mm로 작업하여 총 사이즈는 296mm로 작업하였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bab18c9e-ace6-43c5-8de9-7eb4838284f3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" styl