n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA0MTJfMTQw/MDAxNzQ0NDY0Nzc1MTQz.7L_lNwnlN1MoUlsPl4Cl-FQQFScLg4fYSRbb33E0sLYg.V1f8tHVDO-MraSrfZl7FIddkvciQPkXIMr6GsccDd28g.PNG/2.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-3bdb20e0-bd44-4850-a462-d5a529c75806\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-595cb38a-19e4-40c7-9e33-8beca0db5443\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-88174ee1-5c97-4163-aa6a-d7745f08b389\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-d6e8b071-0987-4d07-ac13-597b36dedc9e\" style=\"\">리플렛 의뢰 시 체크해야 할 사항</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b90cd848-d07b-4027-a281-5785a0daf90e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3662a15d-3914-4a59-8512-c0386e14ade8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5ad1021a-cc90-4dcd-a697-663730ed3acb\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 풍부한 포트폴리오를 경험한 회사인가?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-16c79db8-1f01-40c3-9f57-96776ead8c1e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-42dd0f3e-5ac2-429b-a0d3-d0a0de281058\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d29bd77a-4a4c-4c18-9d68-8632499497ee\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>고객과의 소통이 원활한 회사인가?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7dff4f35-e661-47a2-8f80-fd66703917f2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e78e7386-c8ea-482e-8c88-81c0c0d6a52e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 가격, 품질, 납기를 원하는 때에 제대로 약속을 지킬 수 있는 회사인가?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d6893008-edd3-4c88-9fb6-ead60b224674\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9038009e-c3a8-4554-8967-e6cc35dbbdf3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-755bf1da-3259-42d2-882e-bad1a76a0260\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e585a410-10c7-485e-95e9-9cfa0d8b37ad\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 사항을 체크하여 발주하시는 것이 중요합니다. 하지만 더 중요한 것은 고객님의 준비성입니다. 업체 컨택 전에 다음 사항을 반드시 체크하여 미리미리 본인의 파트를 점검해 보시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9d4169bd-5ecc-4801-b513-63fc24777cb0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4b5b252c-ef76-4f0a-9c51-0155d51a1da5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2f879d65-e34b-4ef6-ab79-f6550c5b26df\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1493a526-6b5b-46e3-809e-a1b5cc5387e7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 만들고자 하는 의도, 또는 컨셉을 정의해 봅니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b6923b78-99d4-4ba3-90ef-75f0dc4835dc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-78970d85-e619-4bbd-849d-8a921e1839eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 가격 예산 혹은 필요한 시기를 조정 또는 유추해 봅니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-afbfd179-ed42-411d-974d-5c557c983458\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1f25108d-500b-43db-8c17-158b8c1f7787\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 디자인이 잘 나올 수 있도록 내부 자료는 준비되어 있는지 확인해 봅니다. 예를 들어 로고, 이미지, 정보, 사양 등의 내부 자료입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-39eec967-acee-49f3-8911-a4d511cffc8e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b9957d68-385d-4c18-a2f8-380a45a5dbd1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-bd46aac2-aac4-40fb-9b81-b0c8c0a48be1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bf907656-88a5-47e6-b851-417a8fe32b31\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-9326f553-7961-41ab-95b4-2847b5735913\" style=\"\">A4 3단 리플렛이 가장 어울리는 업종</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1b7706a0-fb4a-489b-bc30-5c01f293be49\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-77432763-c920-4249-a3ed-656c2c6de61b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-df6df315-1692-44d1-9444-a4804b9d40cf\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 보험/손해사정사</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-889a64a4-cf56-45ca-bd0f-e0983d6cf65b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2f339136-085a-44da-83b6-a14b97c41bd8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ccec8a5f-ce41-4a36-9eee-8f570aca0abe\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>변호사/변리사//법무사</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cd07e64d-fe0b-45c8-a427-68a468b0bf92\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5fddd218-236d-49fd-bab2-1682f38b6237\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 회계사/세무사</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1b80a16f-98b6-4ed9-8e63-d93b32d8e170\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a17ed551-1ea8-45ab-a03b-0746d020237b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-61386c71-ae2d-46d6-b99b-7947212b13c5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f02e8b2e-2d03-4701-b7ed-747debc203f4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위와 같이 전문 직종에 가장 어울립니다. 디자인에서 납기까지 최대한 빠른 시일안에 제작해 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5cf57212-6dc1-48c3-8b2f-a7db1457cb50\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1bb8c1c9-bba1-4f4e-8c86-f9e069d0ed8e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p c